day when I came home.

00:06:50.676 --> 00:06:52.830
And my wife was on
the computer.

00:06:52.830 --> 00:06:53.610
She was working.

00:06:53.610 --> 00:06:57.480
And she had a video window
going, but she wasn't really

00:06:57.480 --> 00:06:59.190
talking to anyone.

00:06:59.190 --> 00:07:00.890
It was just there.

00:07:00.890 --> 00:07:02.430
And she was doing her work.

00:07:02.430 --> 00:07:05.710
I was like, who are you
on a video chat with?

00:07:05.710 --> 00:07:07.590
And she said, it's Arden--

00:07:07.590 --> 00:07:08.870
