00:07:08.870 --> 00:07:11.150
And I was like, where's Arden?

00:07:11.150 --> 00:07:13.210
And she said, well,
he's upstairs.

00:07:13.210 --> 00:07:15.490
So there was a video link
between upstairs and

00:07:15.490 --> 00:07:16.710
