00:07:25.610 --> 00:07:27.880
He's supposed to be up in his
room, but he's lonely.

00:07:27.880 --> 00:07:31.830
And so they just had a video
link between the two of each

00:07:31.830 --> 00:07:34.390
other just to keep each
other company.

00:07:34.390 --> 00:07:38.610
And that made me think about,
when I was in college, I

00:07:38.610 --> 00:07:41.680
couldn't study when I was
sitting alone in my room.

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:44.620
