00:07:45.140 --> 00:07:46.370
And we didn't really talk.

00:07:46.370 --> 00:07:47.630
We just studied together.

00:07:47.630 --> 00:07:51.100
And I was happier and more
productive when I was just

00:07:51.100 --> 00:07:52.100
around people.

00:07:52.100 --> 00:07:55.140
And I noticed that in our
engineering teams also.

00:07:55.140 --> 00:07:57.510
We would be in video
calls together, and

00:07:57.510 --> 00:07:58.120
