say that part of the reason

00:30:07.390 --> 00:30:10.370
why we invest so heavily
internally in technologies

00:30:10.370 --> 00:30:13.230
like Hangouts is to understand
the opportunity for

00:30:13.230 --> 00:30:13.800
enterprises.

00:30:13.800 --> 00:30:16.790
And we've been very encouraged
by the initial results.

00:30:16.790 --> 00:30:20.530
CHEE CHEW: I think that we, for
