a read on the person you're

00:30:35.970 --> 00:30:36.490
talking to.

00:30:36.490 --> 00:30:39.750
So we firmly believe, especially
as distributed as

00:30:39.750 --> 00:30:44.760
Google is, if you use things
like video technology and it's

00:30:44.760 --> 00:30:48.040
high quality, you will make your
business more efficient.

00:30:48.040 --> 00:30:50.726
So we think of it as actually
a competitive advantage.

00:30:50.726 --> 00:30:53.280
NIKHYL SINGHAL: And there's
actually an insight that we

00:30:53.280 --> 00:30:56.730
had early in the launch
