in the public.

00:31:26.260 --> 00:31:29.220
So the notion of an unstructured
conversation in

00:31:29.220 --> 00:31:31.800
the enterprise is actually
a really, really

00:31:31.800 --> 00:31:33.180
ripe area to innovate.

00:31:33.180 --> 00:31:36.300
And I think you'll see the
blending of social and

00:31:36.300 --> 00:31:39.700
enterprise really delivering
on a new style of

00:31:39.700 --> 00:31:41.460
communication that I think we're
just starting to see

