Being inside the video
conversation is heavyweight.

00:42:17.300 --> 00:42:19.660
And usually you have to
have a speaking role.

00:42:19.660 --> 00:42:22.050
Being able to say, I think
that's a great question or

00:42:22.050 --> 00:42:24.610
being able to submit your own
question without coming up to

00:42:24.610 --> 00:42:27.930
the mic in this example, being
able to do that on what we

00:42:27.930 --> 00:42:32.260
call Google Moderator, if you
were to club this together,

00:42:32.260 --> 00:42:36.610
this is the number one ask
from broadcasters today.

00:42:36.610 --> 00:42:39.160
We have a product that's
broadcasting, but it's how can

00:42:39.160 --> 00:42:42.330
I engage the audience that's
watching in addition to engage

00:42:42.330 --> 00:42:44.840
the audience that is
participating?

