certain classes of machines

00:46:39.800 --> 00:46:40.680
and that sort of thing.

00:46:40.680 --> 00:46:43.700
So it takes a lot of
tuning on our part.

00:46:43.700 --> 00:46:45.180
We don't have anything to
announce right now, but

00:46:45.180 --> 00:46:46.760
there's no question that
we're going to be

00:46:46.760 --> 00:46:48.610
moving in that direction.

00:46:48.610 --> 00:46:51.610
One of the things we do also
