time line

00:47:14.610 --> 00:47:15.410
or anything to announce.

00:47:15.410 --> 00:47:18.010
But the philosophy I'd have
you understand is we're

00:47:18.010 --> 00:47:19.590
definitely pushing in
that direction.

00:47:19.590 --> 00:47:22.000
We're going to push the envelope
as hard as we can on

00:47:22.000 --> 00:47:25.640
the overall quality of the
audio and the video.

00:47:25.640 --> 00:47:30.470
But respecting the broad array
of hardware devices that we

00:47:30.470 --> 00:47:32.166
have to support.

