00:48:16.300 --> 00:48:17.335
Create an event.

00:48:17.335 --> 00:48:19.680
It's the special type called
a Hangout Event.

00:48:19.680 --> 00:48:20.550
There'll be a link.

00:48:20.550 --> 00:48:21.740
It'll show up in
