static URL, so I can just
know where to go.

00:49:56.745 --> 00:49:59.010
I know where to go, and I just
have it posted somewhere.

00:49:59.010 --> 00:50:00.760
And I can bookmark it.

00:50:00.760 --> 00:50:02.950
And so with Events, you can
